OL,5, The Vatican has defrocked a US-based   
OL,6, priest for "blasphemous" social media  
OL,7, posts and activism in support of former
OL,8, President Donald Trump.                
OL,10,FA letter to US bishops from the        
OL,11,FVatican's US ambassador accused the    
OL,12,Fpriest, Frank Pavone, of "persistent   
OL,13,Fdisobedience".                         
OL,15,FIn 2016, Mr Pavone, who heads the      
OL,16,Fanti-abortion group Priests for Life,  
OL,17,Fput an aborted foetus on an altar and  
OL,18,Fbroadcast it online.                   
OL,20,FHis defrocking cannot be appealed.     
